nd:linear-gradient(135deg,#0d5c36,#22b068);color:#fff;text-decoration:none;padding:16px 48px;border-radius:100px;font-size:16px;font-weight:700;\">Create My Campaign Now</a></td></tr></table><table width=\"100%\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" style=\"background:#fff9e6;border:1px solid #ffe6a0;border-radius:10px;margin-bottom:20px;\"><tr><td style=\"padding:18px 24px;\"><p style=\"font-size:13px;color:#996600;font-weight:600;margin:0 0 8px;\">⏰ Important - After Creating Your Campaign:</p><p style=\"font-size:13px;color:#7a5200;margin:0;\">Take 10 seconds to mark it complete so we can track your campaign:</p><p style=\"margin:12px 0 0;text-align:center;\"><a href=\"{{ $json.completionUrl }}\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color:#0d5c36;font-weight:600;text-decoration:none;border-bottom:2px solid #0d5c36;\">Mark Campaign Complete</a></p></td></tr></table><p style=\"font-size:12px;color:#999;text-align:center;margin:0;\">Need help? Just reply to this email. We're here to support you!</p></td></tr><tr><td style=\"background:#0d5c36;padding:20px 40px;text-align:center;\"><p style=\"color:rgba(255,255,255,0.6);font-size:12px;margin:0;\">Salaam Masjid Kempston — May Allah bless your fundraising efforts 🤲</p></td></tr></table></td></tr></table></body></html>",
